(286, 1, 1, 8, '<p>S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;Q, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;Q এবং x - y = 2}<br />\r\nQ = {- 2, - 1, 0, 1},&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(m) = {1 + m^3 + m^6\\over m^3}\\)</span></p>\r\n', '[\"<p>P = {x&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\in\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(^2\\\\)</span>&nbsp;+ x - 72= 0} সেটটিকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়কে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে এর ডোমেন নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>দেখাও যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(f(t^2) = f(t^{-2})\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '8', '2022', 1),
(287, 1, 1, 8, '<p>(i) U = {a, b, c, e, f, g}এবং<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; A = {a, b, c, d}, B = {a, e, f, g}<br />\r\n(ii) (x - a, y + 2a) = (y - 2a, 2x + a)</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>যদি A = {x&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\in\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x &lt; 19 এবং x, 3 এর গুনিতক } হয় তবে A সেটকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>(i) নং হতে প্রমান কর যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\((A \\\\cap B)\' = (A - B) \\\\cup (B - A)\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>(ii) নং হতে (x, y) নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '7', '2022', 1),
(288, 1, 1, 8, '<p>(i) P = {5, 6, 7, 8}<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Q = {6, 7, 8, 9}<br />\r\n(ii) S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;B এবং 2x - y = 0}, যেখানে<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; A = {-1, 0, 1}, B = {-2, 2, 4}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>C = {-6, -4, -2, 2, 4, 6} কে সেট গঠন পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\((P \\\\cup Q) = (P - Q) \\\\cup  (Q - P) \\\\cup (P \\\\cap Q)\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়টিকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে এর রেন্জ নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '11', '2022', 1),
(289, 1, 1, 8, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(y) = (1 + y^2 + y^4) \\div y^2 \\)</span>&nbsp;এবং S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A এবং y = 2 - x},<br />\r\nযেখানে, A = {0, 1, 2, 3}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>যদি (x + y, 6) = (0, x - y) হয় তাহলে (x, y) এর মান নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(f(p^{-2}) = f(p^2)\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S কে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর এবং ডোমেন ও রেন্জ নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '10', '2022', 1),
(290, 1, 1, 8, '<p>L = {x : x এবং&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(x^2\\)</span>&nbsp;&lt; 9}<br />\r\nM ={-2, 0, 2}<br />\r\nN = {0, 1, 2}<br />\r\nS = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;L, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;L এবং x - y = 1}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>C = {a, b} এবং D = {a, c} হলে, C - D নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে,&nbsp;M&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N = (M\\\\N)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;(N\\\\M)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;(M&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N)</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়টিকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর এবং এর রেন্জ নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '12', '2020', 1),
(291, 1, 1, 8, '<p>S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A এবং 2x - y = 1}<br />\r\nA = {0, 1, 2, 3}, B = y - 3x</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>f(x) = x<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(^2\\\\)</span>&nbsp;- 4x + 3 হলে f(-1) নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়কে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে তার রেন্জ নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>B = 0 এর লেখচিত্র অঙ্কন করে এটি ফাংশন কি না তা যাচাই কর, যেখানে -2&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\leq\\\\)</span>&nbsp;x&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\leq\\\\)</span>&nbsp;2</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '5', '2020', 1),
(292, 1, 1, 8, '<p>সার্বিক সেট&nbsp; U = {x : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N এবং x<sup>2&nbsp;</sup>&lt; 53}<br />\r\nA = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x মৈালিক সংখ্যা এবং x&lt;10}<br />\r\nB ={4, 5}&nbsp;এবং<br />\r\nC = {&nbsp;x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;&gt; 7 এবং x<sup>3</sup> &lt; 136}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>A ও C সেটকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে, (A&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;B)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;(B&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;C) = (A&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;B)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;C</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>P(B&#39; - A&#39;) নির্নয় কর।<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '7', '2020', 2),
(293, 1, 1, 8, '<p>A = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;- 10x + 24 = 0),<br />\r\nf(x) = x<sup>4</sup>&nbsp;+ 3x<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;+ Px<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;- 3x - 4 + P, <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(g(y) = {3y + 1 \\over 3y -1}\\)</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>P(A) নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>P এর মান কত হলে, f(-2) = 0 হবে তা নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(g(y - 2) + 1 \\\\over g(y -2) -1\\\\)</span>&nbsp;েএর মান নির্নয় কর</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '11', '2020', 2),
(294, 1, 1, 8, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(x) = {5x^2 + 3\\over 5x^2 - 3}\\)</span>&nbsp;S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;C, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;D এবং 2x + y &lt; 10},<br />\r\nC = {1, 3, 5} এবং D = {2, 4, 7}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>f(x) = <span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(x^4\\\\)</span>&nbsp;+ 5x -3 হলে f(2) এর মান কত?</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(f({1\\\\over t^2}) +1 \\\\over f({1\\\\over t^2}) -1\\\\)</span>&nbsp;এর মান নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়টিকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে&nbsp;েএর ডোমেন নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '4', '2019', 2),
(295, 1, 1, 8, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(x) = {5x^2 + 3\\over 5x^2 - 3}\\)</span>&nbsp;S = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;C, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;D এবং 2x + y &lt; 10},<br />\r\nC = {1, 3, 5} এবং D = {2, 4, 7}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>f(x) = <span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(x^4\\\\)</span>&nbsp;+ 5x -3 হলে f(2) এর মান কত?</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(f({1\\\\over t^2}) +1 \\\\over f({1\\\\over t^2}) -1\\\\)</span>&nbsp;এর মান নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S অন্বয়টিকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে&nbsp;েএর ডোমেন নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '4', '2019', 2),
(296, 1, 1, 8, '<p>A = {2, 4, 7}, B = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;Z : -2&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\leq\\)</span>&nbsp;x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\leq\\)</span>&nbsp;2} এবং<br />\r\nS = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;B, y<strong>&nbsp;</strong><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;B এবং y - 2x = 0}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>C = {x&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\in\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N P:&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(x^2\\\\)</span>&nbsp;- 9 =0} সেটকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>P(A) নির্নয় করে &ldquo;কোন সেট A এর উপাদান সংখ্যা n হলে, P(A) এর উপাদান সংখ্যা&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(2^n\\\\)</span> হবে&rdquo;- উক্তির সত্যতা যাচাই কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>S&nbsp; অন্বয়কে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ করে ডোমেন নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '8', '2019', 2),
(297, 1, 1, 8, '<p>সার্বিক সেট&nbsp; U = {1, 2, 3, 4, b, c, d}, M = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x<sup><span style=\"font-size:10.8333px\">3</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:10.8333px\">&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\geq\\)</span></span>&nbsp;8 এবং x<sup>4</sup>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.8333px\"><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\leq\\)</span>&nbsp;256},</span><br />\r\nN = { y : y<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;-(c + d) y + cd = 0}&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(x) = {5x - 7 \\over 2x - 3}\\)</span></p>\r\n', '[\"<p>A = {11, 20}, B = {20, a} হলে P(A&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;B) নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>উদ্দিপকের আলোকে দেখাও যে, (M&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N)&#39; = M&#39;&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;N&#39;</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>উদ্দিপকের আলোকে&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\({f(x^{-1}) + 2 \\\\over {f(x^{-1}) - 1}} =3\\\\)</span>&nbsp;হলে, x এর মান নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '9', '2019', 2);
