(298, 1, 1, 8, '<p>(i)&nbsp; &nbsp;A&nbsp; = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;Z : 1&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\leq\\)</span>&nbsp;x<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\leq\\)</span>&nbsp;7} এবং R = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A এবং y - 2x - 1 = 0}&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n(ii)&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(f(x) = { 1 \\over x - 1}\\)</span></p>\r\n', '[\"<p>Q = {x, y} হলে, P(Q) নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>উদ্দিপকের আলোকে (i) থেকে R এর রেন্জ নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>(ii) নং হতে দেখাও যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(f(m) - f(n) \\\\neq f ({mn \\\\over n - m})\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '6', '2019', 2),
