(305, 1, 1, 8, '<p>A = {1, 2, 3}, B = {x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N : x<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp; 15 এবং x<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;&lt; 200}, C = {3, 5, 6} এবং<br />\r\nR = {(x, y) : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A, y&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;A এবং y = x + 1}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>B সেটকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>R কে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর এবং ডোম R ও রেন্জ R নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে, A \\\\(B&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;C) = (A \\\\ B)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;(A \\\\ C)</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '11', '2017', 1),
