(308, 1, 1, 15, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(a=cos\\theta\\)</span> এবং <span class=\"math-tex\">\\(b=cot\\theta\\)</span></p>\r\n', '[\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(sin(90^0-\\\\theta)={\\\\sqrt 3\\\\over2}\\\\)</span> হলে, b এর মান নির্ণয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(b^4-b^2=1 \\\\)</span> হলে, দেখাও যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(a^4+a^2=1\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\({a+b\\\\over a-b}={\\\\sqrt 3+2\\\\over\\\\sqrt 3-2}\\\\)</span>&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\theta\\\\)</span>&nbsp;সূক্ষকোণ হলে,&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\theta\\\\)</span> এর মান নির্ণয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '4', '2022', 2),
