(310, 1, 1, 15, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(cot\\theta+cos\\theta=a\\)</span>&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(cot\\theta-cos\\theta=b\\)</span></p>\r\n', '[\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\theta=60^0\\\\)</span>&nbsp;হলে, b এর মান নির্ণয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>দেখাও যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(a^2+b^2=2cot^2\\\\theta(1+sin^2\\\\theta)\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমাণ করযে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\((a^2-b^2)^2=16ab\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '4', '2022', 2),
(311, 1, 1, 8, '<p>A = {x : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N এবং x<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;- 5x + 6 = 0}<br />\r\nB = {x : x&nbsp;<span class=\"math-tex\">\\(\\in\\)</span>&nbsp;N এবং 2 &lt; x &lt; 6}<br />\r\nC = {2, 4, 6}</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>A সেটকে তালিকা পদ্ধতিতে প্রকাশ কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>প্রমান কর যে, (A\\\\B)&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;(B\\\\A) = (A&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cup\\\\)</span>&nbsp;B) \\\\ (A&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(\\\\cap\\\\)</span>&nbsp;B)</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p>P(B) নির্নয় কর। B এর উপাদান সংখ্যা n হলে, দেখাও যে, P(B) এর উপাদান সংখ্যা&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(2^n\\\\)</span>&nbsp;কে সমর্থন করে।</p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '7', '2016', 1),
