(336, 1, 1, 9, '<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\(x^4 - x^2 + 1 = 0\\)</span>&nbsp;এবং p = 18</p>\r\n', '[\"<p>উৎপাদকে বিশ্লেষন কর:&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(4a^2 + {1\\\\over 4a^2} - 2 + 4a - {1\\\\over a}\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(x^5 + {1\\\\over x^5}\\\\)</span>&nbsp;এর মান&nbsp;&zwj;নির্নয় কর।</p>\\r\\n\",\"<p><span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(p = a^3 + {1\\\\over a^3}\\\\)</span>&nbsp;হলে, প্রমান কর যে,&nbsp;<span class=\\\"math-tex\\\">\\\\(a =  {3 + \\\\sqrt5 \\\\over 2}\\\\)</span></p>\\r\\n\",\"\"]', '', '6', '2020', 1),
