(449, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Rahim and you have a friend named Karim who cannot speak English well. But he wants to be fluent in English. Write an email advising him what he should do to be well conversant in English.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
