(453, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to your friend inviting him to join a picnic.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(454, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Nasim/Nasima. Your friend, Mina/Rajo has lost his/her father. Now, write a letter to your friend condoling him/her. </strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(455, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Mili/Milon living in Comilla. Now, write a letter to your father who lives abroad describing your preparation for the upcoming Test Examination.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(456, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to your younger brother advising him to be punctual.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(457, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you went to visit one of the historical places in Bangladesh on a family tour. Now, write an e-mail to your friend describing the visit. &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(458, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an email to your friend inviting him to the marriage ceremony of your sister. &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(459, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to your younger brother describing the bad effects of smoking.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(460, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Zinia and your little sister is Jesika. Write her an e-mail suggesting the importance of knowledge in ICT. &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(461, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Rupom living in Dhaka. A few days ago you made a plane journey from Dhaka to Rajshahi. Now, send an email to your friend Sumon describing your experience about the journey.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(462, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Roni/Rani. Your younger brother lives in Comilla. Now, write a letter to your brother to avoid bad company.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(463, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Rana/Rani. Your friend is Rahi/Rahela who lives in Mirpur-2, Dhaka-1216. He wanted to know the harmful effects of drug addiction. Write a letter to him/her about it. </strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(464, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Altaf. Your younger brother is Shamim. Write an e-mail to your younger brother about the negative effects of drug addiction.</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(465, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you have participated in the Intra-College Wall Magazine Competition and won the second prize recently. Now, compose an e-mail to your father informing him of your success in the competition.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(466, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Your friend Riyad/Royena finds pleasure in spending his/her off-time visiting friends and relatives. This year the winter vacation of his/her college will begin on the same date as yours. You desire that your friend should come to your house during the winter vacation and spend it in your midst. Now, writer a letter to your friend Riyad/Royena inviting him/her to spend the winter vacation with you.</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(467, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you want to study in a college abroad. You need some information about how to get admission there. Also you need to know about the tuition fees, accommodation facilities etc. Now send an e-mail, to the Admission Officer, Linda College asking for the above information. Send your e-mail to admission@liada.sc.uk&nbsp; &nbsp; </strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(468, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Ihilam. You stayed at your close friend Biren&#39;s house for a week as part of your summer vacation trip. You are now back home and feel overwhelmed with admiration as you reminisce your stay there. Now, write a letter of thanks to Biren for his hospitality.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(469, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an E-mail to your friend condoling him on his father&#39;s death.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(470, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write a letter to your friend about a book you have recently read and enjoyed.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(471, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Samin/Samina. You have just received a letter form your mother. She wanted to know about your life in the hostel. Now, write a reply to the letter.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(472, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to your friend inviting him to join the picnic.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(473, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Shapla and you live in the college hostel. Now, write an email to your friend Nishi describing your hostel life. Don&#39;t forget to send some photos snapped with your hotel mates in the mail attachment.&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(474, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to Admission Officer, International Service, 353 South Road, Sydney, Australia asking about admission procedure for overseas student.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(475, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an email to your friend informing him/her about your preparation for HSC examination.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(476, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Nahid or Nahida and you are a candidate of HSC Examination. Now, send an&nbsp;<br />\r\ne-mail to your father telling him about your progress of studies.&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(477, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Tomal. You have booked an air ticket to visit Thailand. But for some inevitable circumstances you want to cancel the booking. Now, write an e-mail to the director of the Travel Agency to cancel the ticket. </strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(478, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Imagine, you are Junayed. Your friend Rasel missed the English class yesterday. Now, write an e-mail to your friend about what lessons were taught in the class yesterday.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(479, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you need the English version of HSC certificate for admission in a foreign university. Now, write an e-mail to the controller of Dhaka Board to issue you the English version of HSC certificate and send that to your father&#39;s address.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(480, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Sagor. Your younger brother Jubair is going to participate in a debate competition. The topic of the debate is creative question pattern makes students dependent more on guides than textbooks.&quot; He sent you an e-mail asking your assistance in finding necessary information against the aforementioned topic. Now, write an e-mail replying him.</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; 5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(481, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Write an e-mail to admission section of a university asking about admission procedure for overseas students.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(482, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>Suppose, you are Himika, a student of Class XII. Your Test examination is knocking at the door. Now, write a letter to your father about your progress of studies. &nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
(483, 2, 20, 91, '<p><strong>an e-mail to a bank manager to know the procedure to open a savings account.&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp;5</p>\r\n', '', NULL, '', 1),
